== Overview ==
Generating a broad and continuous spectrum stream of ions, the Rc14 Pulse Streamer can disrupt several enemy power centers at once.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Pulse Streamer can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
